OL,3,C'It's time to pay up', says Starmer in
OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,FFirms which persistently pay their
OL,7,Fsuppliers late are set to face fines
OL,8,Fworth potentially millions of pounds
OL,9,Fas the Prime Minister warned that
OL,10,F"it's time to pay up".
OL,12,FSir Keir Starmer has said "too many
OL,13,Fhardworking people are being forced to
OL,14,Fspend precious hours chasing payments"
OL,15,Fin a process which he described as
OL,16,F"exhausting".
