OL,3,C'It's time to pay up', says Starmer in
OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,FAs part of a drive to support small
OL,7,Fbusinesses, the Government is set to
OL,8,Funveil plans to give the small
OL,9,Fbusiness commissioner bolstered powers
OL,10,Fto fine large companies which
OL,11,Fpersistently pay their suppliers late.
OL,13,FThe commissioner will also receive new
OL,14,Fpowers to enforce a rule that
OL,15,Fcustomers must pay their supplier
OL,16,Fwithin 30 days of receiving a valid
OL,17,Finvoice, unless otherwise agreed, with
OL,18,Fspot checks to help identify breaches.
