OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,FUpcoming legislation will also
OL,7,Fintroduce maximum payment terms of 60
OL,8,Fdays, reducing to 45 days.
OL,10,F"From builders and electricians to
OL,11,Ffreelance designers and manufacturers
OL,12,F` too many hardworking people are
OL,13,Fbeing forced to spend precious hours
OL,14,Fchasing payments instead of doing what
OL,15,Fthey do best ` growing their
OL,16,Fbusinesses," Sir Keir said.
OL,18,F"It's unfair, it's exhausting and it's
OL,19,Fholding Britain back.
