OL,3,C'It's time to pay up', says Starmer in
OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,F"So, our message is clear, it's time
OL,7,Fto pay up.
OL,9,F"Through our small business plan,
OL,10,Fwe're not only tackling the scourge of
OL,11,Flate payments once and for all, but
OL,12,Fwe're giving small business owners the
OL,13,Fbacking and stability they need for
OL,14,Ftheir business to thrive, driving
OL,15,Fgrowth across the country through our
OL,16,Fplan for change."
