OL,3,C'It's time to pay up', says Starmer in
OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,FThe crackdown on late payments is part
OL,7,Fof a wider Government package and sits
OL,8,Falongside a move to pump #4 billion of
OL,9,Ffinancial support into small business
OL,10,Fstart-ups and growth.
OL,12,FThis is set to include #1 billion for
OL,13,Fnew firms, with 69,000 start-up loans
OL,14,Fand mentoring support.
