OL,3,C'It's time to pay up', says Starmer in
OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,F"This country is home to some of the
OL,7,Fbrightest entrepreneurs and innovative
OL,8,Fbusinesses in the world, and we want
OL,9,Fto unleash their full potential by
OL,10,Fgiving them back time and money to do
OL,11,Fwhat they do best ` growing our local
OL,12,Feconomies," Business Secretary
OL,13,FJonathan Reynolds said.
OL,15,F"Our small business plan ` the first
OL,16,Fin over a decade ` is slashing
OL,17,Funnecessary admin costs, making it
OL,18,Feasier for businesses to set up shop
OL,19,Fand giving SMEs (small and medium-
OL,20,Fsized enterprises) the financial
OL,21,Fbacking they need."
