OL,4,Clate payments crackdown
OL,6,FAndrew Griffith, the Conservative
OL,7,Fshadow business secretary, said:
OL,8,F"Cracking down on late payments will
OL,9,Fbe welcome for small business but will
OL,10,Fmean nothing for the 218,000
OL,11,Fbusinesses that have closed under
OL,12,FLabour.
OL,14,F"The reality for businesses under
OL,15,FLabour is a doubling of business
OL,16,Frates, a #25 billion jobs tax and a
OL,17,Ffull-on strangulation of employment
OL,18,Fred tape.
